extendedInfo.description: Hot Rod Magazine's #1 Rated Practice-Tree App!There was a time when going head to head meant you had to draw quick to stay alive. Now you have to react quick to stay competitive. JEGS Perfect Start is a reaction time game that keeps you at your fastest. See if you can beat your best time or challenge a friend to beat your time. Try Pro or Sportsman mode, set your Reaction Time Delay and see how fast you really are; go for a Perfect Start (.000)!Whether you are a racer looking for a competitive edge or a fan lookingto catch a glimpse grab this App...Ready, set, go!Features:* Sportsman/Full practice Tree (.500)* Pro practice tree settings (.400)* Adjustable Reaction Time Delay to simulate vehicleTry Pro or Sportsmanmode, set your Reaction Time Delay and see how fast you really are; gofor a Perfect Start (.000)!Practice your Perfect Start. Hold the JEGS button down until the tree begins to cycle. Release the button to clock your time.Adjust your Roll Out/Reaction Time Delay - Press options and dial in your desired time (0.000 - 1.500).

reviews.title: The Best of the smart phone Trees.
reviews.comment: As a Bracket racer who is always trying to stay sharp on the tree this is the ABSOLUTE BEST of the downloadable applications for smart phones, and in fact have seen several of the Pro guys using theirs between rounds like Vincent Nobile and Spencer Massey just to name a couple and thats how I found out about it.  I figure if its good enough for them it should be great for me. Leave it to JEGS to come up with a free version to help racers anywhere who has a smart phone.
